"Reports from the scene allege that the farmer had been assaulted by a group of men and he had sustained several injuries including a fracture to his left arm. The man is believed to be approximately 55 years old. He was stabilised by paramedics at the scene before being transported by Netcare 911 to hospital for further assessment and care."
